<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1006809' id='t-1006809'>and then you keep it a little bit longer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1009169' id='t-1009169'>and when you keep it that long,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1010689' id='t-1010689'>I'm sure some of you now
have noticed the cow.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1013453' id='t-1013453'>Some of you have seen the flag.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1015487' id='t-1015487'>Some of you start wondering,
is the farmer at home?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1017893' id='t-1017893'>Has he left? Is he watching the cow?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1020340' id='t-1020340'>And where is that cow going?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1023567' id='t-1023567'>So my point is, the longer
